{"tid":1868691,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求做保育相關行業巴打入黎?","createTime":"2020-02-07T17:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T15:38:14.000Z","uid":174171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb862b1a761a3586532fb3b92f5bfa55718b045","tid":1868691,"uid":174171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"一直對 ecology 同 environmental science 有興趣 但degree最後揀左engine <br />\n而家畢業後做左幾年野想返轉頭追夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有冇巴打係讀相關科目或做緊類似嘅野可以比d建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家下諗緊應該讀master洗底定做相關義工接觸下呢行先"},{"pid":"23fa0dacaa426a46b5ae4cc79239ea3de7edfe48","tid":1868691,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"巴打養埋我，我陪你讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9d8880ed197c03eb957a17f9b11bd019bd1807","tid":1868691,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T18:58:29.000Z","msg":"諗住讀咩Master<br />\n做到乞食咁其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2044e8471e788c5ee751062b2b96abae7b81b75","tid":1868691,"uid":174171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23fa0dacaa426a46b5ae4cc79239ea3de7edfe48","tid":1868691,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"巴打養埋我，我陪你讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"巴打讀緊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0c099b67033559fe691441da65807fdd2aa723","tid":1868691,"uid":174171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad9d8880ed197c03eb957a17f9b11bd019bd1807","tid":1868691,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020